  "id": "RAW_747f66e2",
  "title": "「数字 AGI」已死？亚马逊内部重组，撕掉纯算法派最后的遮羞布",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI3MTA0MTk1MA==&mid=2652657511&idx=3&sn=8af70464a30370a3d569be851103b051",
  "date": "2025-12-24 10:32:00",
  "author": "新智元",
  "siteName": "新智元",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <h3 data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505172243\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.42578125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/UicQ7HgWiaUb013ZfdanZicnVwibkWkHEZdtUJJMS942yuMXHhKhu43Vh8cPY5WNZHEiawXeDoxFYRsORWJ249Lcphg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"247\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"246\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b8711df7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb013ZfdanZicnVwibkWkHEZdtUJJMS942yuMXHhKhu43Vh8cPY5WNZHEiawXeDoxFYRsORWJ249Lcphg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <h3 style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">新智元报道 &nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：倾倾</span></span></p>\n  <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></p>\n    <h5 style=\"padding:10px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;word-break:break-all !important;margin-top:10px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">【新智元导读】</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">拒绝平庸的对话框，亚马逊正亲手撕碎AI的次元壁！「工程沙皇」DeSantis联合「机器人宗师」Abbeel，将芯片、模型与钢铁躯壳暴力缝合。这不是在更新软件，这是在锻造 AGI 的物理真身！巨头觉醒，闭环已成，实体 AI 时代正式降临！</span></span></strong></span></h5>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">很长一段时间里，大众对AGI的想象，被压缩成了一个对话框。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">就在昨天，亚马逊CEO Andy Jassy宣布了一次罕见的组织调整：将Nova大模型团队、自研芯片部门与量子计算研究整合进同一体系。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" data-asynid=\"\" src=\"https://qzqs9kyge0.feishu.cn/space/api/box/stream/download/asynccode/?code=MjE1N2MxM2FiMjhmYzk5MTc2YWIxN2M0ZDFhNjkwYjFfM0JHVnpBOHFwU0RwY3V3cHd1Q1E5U1pVT3o0WFBNVE1fVG9rZW46V3VvWWJuMXFPb2RUM294ZjUzMWMxeTVEbkZmXzE3NjYwMzkyMjI6MTc2NjA0MjgyMl9WNA\" data-src=\"\" align=\"\" alt=\"\" border=\"\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"\" data-s=\"\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"\" aria-label=\"\" aria-braillelabel=\"\" aria-description=\"\" height=\"\" hspace=\"\" ismap opacity=\"\" sizes=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" title=\"\" type=\"\" usemap=\"\" vspace=\"\" width=\"\" data-width=\"1418\" data-height=\"650\" data-croporisrc=\"\" data-cropx1=\"\" data-cropx2=\"\" data-cropy1=\"\" data-cropy2=\"\" data-cropselx1=\"\" data-cropselx2=\"\" data-cropsely1=\"\" data-cropsely2=\"\" data-backw=\"\" data-backh=\"\" data-copyright=\"\" data-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-before-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-gallerysupplier=\"\" data-cardimg=\"\" data-fileid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"505172260\" data-positionback=\"\" data-imgqrcoded=\"\" data-imgid=\"\" data-upload=\"\" data-fromlib=\"\" data-aiimageid=\"\" data-aiimagesource=\"\" data-cacheurl=\"\" data-retry=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505172265\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.45839210155148097\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1418\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1418\" data-height=\"650\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"258\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d3e4c7b7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb013ZfdanZicnVwibkWkHEZdtbN6EhWnmwQ4Q79RBYSHJwjWUrTSYS2CbYtKiamIicE1tSyJFQ66uibbsw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">几乎同时，机器人与强化学习领域的代表人物Pieter Abbeel，正式进入亚马逊AGI体系。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">与其继续在云端堆叠参数，亚马逊选择把算力、模型与物理世界放进同一张设计图里。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在亚马逊看来，AGI不应只是一个会聊天的文人，而是一个拥有芯片为骨、算法为魂的「物理实体」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">算力不再是资源，权力才是</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">亚马逊选择由老将Peter DeSantis统筹这一轮整合。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505172263\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"200\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"200\" data-height=\"200\" data-backw=\"200\" data-backh=\"200\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9fd2803c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb013ZfdanZicnVwibkWkHEZdthRG5mDh71Rv1YMoibhYHKOJDdJyBIGPicTJxBJSXkRtC66Jw0miaHZlIA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">DeSantis在内部以极强的工程交付能力著称，他不仅是云基础设施的掌舵人，更是亚马逊自研芯片计划的幕后推手。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这一任命意味着，AGI不再只是模型团队的研究课题，而被视作一项需要长期工程投入的系统工程。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在外界看来，将AGI团队、自研芯片部门与量子计算强行缝合显得臃肿，但在亚马逊看来，这是事关算力主权的决定。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在AGI竞赛的下半场，算法的领先往往只有几个月的窗口期，而成本的领先才是永久的护城河。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">长期以来，硅谷巨头们都深陷Nvidia的产能焦虑中，而亚马逊试图通过垂直整合来打破这种被动。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">其自研的Trainium 2系列芯片已经证明了其在训练性能和能效比上的野心。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AGI团队+芯片团队，能让Nova模型的每一行底层代码，都能在自研芯片上实现「像素级」的优化。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Nova模型结构示意</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这种深度适配，就像苹果独树一帜的M系列芯片一样。让亚马逊能以远低于对手的成本，驱动复杂的Amazon Nova模型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">对亚马逊而言，算力不只是资源问题，而是战略边界。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">Pieter Abbeel 与 AGI 的下一步形态</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如果说架构重组是「骨架」，那么Pieter Abbeel的加盟，则是为这具躯壳注入了的「灵魂」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">过去两年里，大模型的能力提升，越来越依赖规模扩张，而非范式跃迁。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">亚马逊之所以重金请他出山，是因为AGI的竞赛正面临一个巨大的隐性瓶颈：互联网上的高质量文本数据快被用光了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Pieter Abbeel是机器人学习与强化学习领域的关键人物之一。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">作为UC Berkeley教授，他在机器人学习和强化学习方向拥有长期的学术积累，并培养出多位影响当代大模型研究的重要人物。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505172264\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.738\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"500\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"369\" data-backw=\"500\" data-backh=\"369\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=30596d85&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb013ZfdanZicnVwibkWkHEZdtgHwXFLWyxTbMPlWZq5YatEibylEvxH2K6p2icbmiapbq1P1rgVegxIyeA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当大多数模型还在虚拟的字符世界里打转时，Abbeel带来的是关于「真实世界」的钥匙。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Abbeel认为，AI的最终进化必须通过与物理世界的实时互动来实现。这就是所谓的「具身智能」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而亚马逊恰好拥有全球最庞大的物流仓储，以及成千上万台Proteus自主移动机器人。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">不同于实验室里的研究型机器人，这些系统运行在高度标准化、却规模极端庞大的真实环境中。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">亚马逊首款全自动移动机器人</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">对于Abbeel来说，这些正是收集物理规律数据的完美样本。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在他的研究框架中，AGI的终极形态并不局限于屏幕。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在亚马逊的规划里，AGI不应只是一个润色邮件的秘书，而是一个能听懂模糊指令、能感知重力与摩擦力、能在混乱的仓库甚至家庭环境中精准抓取物品的「超级劳动力」。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505172267\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6694444444444444\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1440\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1440\" data-height=\"964\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"376\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=81def93d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb013ZfdanZicnVwibkWkHEZdtbMsda8wYmVoRy4PpGxvaKayneT0WmUsRNTw9Pa3EH44c9d3ScdvAJQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当Nova模型的逻辑推理与Abbeel的物理操控技术结合，AGI将进化成「无所不能的工匠」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这种从云端到指尖的闭环，让亚马逊正在定义的AGI展现出一种前所未有的厚重感。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它不再漂浮于比特世界，而是扎根于钢铁与算法之中。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">别人还在卷模型，亚马逊换了一条赛道</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">放在更大的行业格局中看，亚马逊的选择显得格外不同。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">一是以微软和OpenAI为代表的「云端智慧」派，他们拥有最强的逻辑推演能力，却始终被困在屏幕之后，缺乏与物理世界交互的能力；</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">二是以谷歌为代表的「全能选手」派，虽然坐拥DeepMind的技术积淀，却受困于内部组织的割裂，难以将尖端算法与硬件制造完成真正的闭环。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而亚马逊正在走的，是第三条路：</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">以场景倒逼模型，以闭环重塑生态。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这条路径的前提，是否拥有足够多、足够真实、足够长期运行的物理场景。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">对比OpenAI这种纯粹的软件巨头，亚马逊最大的优势在于——它在全球拥有的超过 75 万台工业机器人。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在硅谷，训练数据往往需要被购买和清洗；而在亚马逊，物理世界本身就是持续运行的数据源。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505172269\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2000\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"2000\" data-height=\"1125\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"316\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9019e767&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb013ZfdanZicnVwibkWkHEZdt3SDAkwXStq7USbMZaiby6R43qa6SzN5qr9dyZbiccUXroicfJGXiadIe5A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当对手还在通过Reddit上的帖子来教AI理解世界时，亚马逊已经可以通过分布在全球的自动化中心，利用现实中的重力、阻力和摩擦力数据，来训练一个真正理解物理法则的AGI。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这条路彰显了亚马逊的商业傲慢，也是它的终极底气。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如果AGI最终必须服务于实体经济，那么掌握了物理场景的人，就掌握了规则的制定权。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">光是「重资产」的竞争门槛，就让那些单纯依赖第三方算力、缺乏物理落地场景的初创公司，在这场长跑中陷入被动。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">AGI，正在进入大工业时代</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Pieter Abbeel与Peter DeSantis，不单是普通的人事变动，更是预示着AI行业将要发生的</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">权力转移</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">长期以来，AI的进步严重依赖于实验室里的个人英雄主义和算法巧思。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但随着Amazon Nova这类工业级模型的普及，以及对Trainium 2这种大规模算力底座的渴求，AI竞赛的门槛已经发生了质变。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">我们正在目睹「实验室时代」的落幕，以及「大工业时代」的开启。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">未来的AGI将只属于极少数能够实现「全栈闭环」的巨头。这种闭环不仅仅是代码的闭环，更是「算力-大脑-身体」的物理闭环。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">亚马逊的豪赌，定义了一个冷峻的新现实：如果AGI的下半场是具身智能，那么谁拥有最廉价的算力主权，谁拥有最真实的物理交互数据，谁就握住了通往未来的入场券。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505172268\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1200\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1200\" data-height=\"675\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"316\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=76dcd1e2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb013ZfdanZicnVwibkWkHEZdtia8FqPMLjctc6iaPFzGicpNSROss29z08icFL0qPibRkuDGtesV1OoBdTGA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">从这一刻开始，AGI的竞争，已经不再是所有公司都能参与的游戏。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">与其反复讨论AI是否会替代某种具体工作，不如关注另一件事：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当AGI穿上钢铁盔甲走出实验室时，它将彻底重构人类与物理世界的关系。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而那一天，正随着亚马逊的这场权力大重组，加速到来。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">参考资料：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\">\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;\"><a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-12-17/amazon-names-new-ai-chief-amid-battle-to-take-on-tech-rivals?srnd=phx-technology\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-12-17/amazon-names-new-ai-chief-amid-battle-to-take-on-tech-rivals?srnd=phx-technology</a></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;\"><a href=\"https://x.com/bookwormengr/status/2001353147055509881https://www.cnbc.com/2025/12/17/amazon-ai-chief-prasad-leaving-peter-desantis-agi-group.htmlhttps://www.reuters.com/technology/amazon-taps-veteran-peter-desantis-lead-ai-chip-quantum-push-2025-12-17/https://www.businessinsider.com/amazon-agi-executive-leaving-ai-models-rohit-prasad-2025-12\" target=\"_blank\">https://x.com/bookwormengr/status/2001353147055509881https://www.cnbc.com/2025/12/17/amazon-ai-chief-prasad-leaving-peter-desantis-agi-group.htmlhttps://www.reuters.com/technology/amazon-taps-veteran-peter-desantis-lead-ai-chip-quantum-push-2025-12-17/https://www.businessinsider.com/amazon-agi-executive-leaving-ai-models-rohit-prasad-2025-12</a></span></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "亚马逊通过整合大模型、自研芯片、量子计算和机器人团队，引入机器人学习专家 Pieter Abbeel，致力于构建具备物理交互能力的“具身智能”AGI，打破传统 AI 的次元壁。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "亚马逊通过整合大模型、自研芯片、量子计算和机器人团队，引入机器人学习专家 Pieter Abbeel，致力于构建具备物理交互能力的“具身智能”AGI，打破传统 AI 的次元壁。",
  "summary": "文章深入分析了亚马逊近期在 AGI（通用人工智能）领域的重大战略调整。亚马逊 CEO Andy Jassy 宣布将 Nova 大模型团队、自研芯片部门与量子计算研究整合，并引入机器人与强化学习专家 Pieter Abbeel。这一举措表明亚马逊正从单纯的“云端智慧”转向构建具备物理实体的 AGI，强调算力、模型与物理世界的闭环。文章指出，亚马逊通过自研芯片解决算力成本问题，并利用其庞大的物流仓储和工业机器人作为具身智能的天然训练场。这种“以场景倒逼模型，以闭环重塑生态”的策略，使亚马逊在 AGI 竞争中走向一条与微软/OpenAI、谷歌不同的道路，预示着 AGI 将进入“大工业时代”，只属于少数能实现“算力-大脑-身体”物理闭环的巨头。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
